<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَأَمَرَ بِالْقُنُوتِ فِي النِّصْفِ الْأَخِيرِ مِنْهُ.<span class="c5"> وَلَنَا قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="special">﵊</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>